      "content": "i guess. but it feels different than just being lonely. it feels like i'm already dead, you know? like i'm just a ghost in a chair. if i actually did something about it, if i just... stopped existing... would it even be a tragedy? or would it just be like a glitch in the system that everyone ignores?",
